    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绝尘》是一款融入了高丰富度动作系统的武侠题材的横版动作冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demo包含了第一章的部分内容，您将在此demo中体验到出色的战斗系统、复杂的地图设计和激动人心的Boss战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在剑冢中苏醒却失去记忆的一人一剑，走入潜藏阴谋与杀机的荆棘之路，在历程中逐渐寻回二者散落的魂魄，忆起自己的真实身份。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/c41ca05cb960aecf06eadd389cdcfbd6.avif?t=1749707101\" width=608 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用我流手绘风格美术，结合高帧率逐帧动画，塑造出独特鲜明的视觉表现。高质量的逐帧动画不仅让角色动作更加细腻流畅，也赋予整体画面强烈的生命力与表现力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/96ada07ad9d2b235e8b4eb8526a5ebc7.poster.avif?t=1749707101\" width=614 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/96ada07ad9d2b235e8b4eb8526a5ebc7.webm?t=1749707101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/96ada07ad9d2b235e8b4eb8526a5ebc7.mp4?t=1749707101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/519cd498a950710952628f031c5d28bd.avif?t=1749707101\" width=608 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索环环相扣的回廊式地图，在落雪池、识月阁、天门、画中界等独具特色的关卡中遨游，每个关卡都有丰富的可探索元素与新机制，地图之间会以回廊结构呈现，后续关卡解锁的能力可用于解锁前序关卡难以通行的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/e764d5a314df572239b57a06c25c6944.poster.avif?t=1749707101\" width=614 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/e764d5a314df572239b57a06c25c6944.webm?t=1749707101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/e764d5a314df572239b57a06c25c6944.mp4?t=1749707101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/5e392aeeb2510b16e32ec27269f3c7df.avif?t=1749707101\" width=608 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在2D平台游戏的玩法基础上，融合了格挡反击、拼刀等侠客决斗应有的要素，鼓励玩家与敌人正面对抗、硬碰硬。剑技、灵宝、神识、绝招等多种战斗系统相互配合，让玩家在实战中自由施展招式，体验武侠中以技克敌、过招切磋的乐趣。爽快流畅的打击节奏也进一步增强了战斗的沉浸感与爽感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/696fb33ee60b97f5a5d7c537bb6ba221.poster.avif?t=1749707101\" width=614 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/696fb33ee60b97f5a5d7c537bb6ba221.webm?t=1749707101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156480/extras/696fb33ee60b97f5a5d7c537bb6ba221.mp4?t=1749707101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
